Error
Critical vulnerabilities found

Pipeline blocked


What Actually Happens
Pipeline scans:

Docker images
OS packages
Application dependencies
before deployment.

Troubleshooting
Reviewed vulnerability report
Identified vulnerable package
Updated base image
Resolution
