10) CI/CD Pipeline Performance Issues
Real-Time Scenario
Pipeline execution time increased from 10 minutes to 45 minutes.

Root Cause
Large Docker images
No caching
Sequential execution
Resolution
Implemented:

Docker layer caching
Parallel stages
Incremental builds
Shared workspace caching
Result
Reduced pipeline execution time from 45 minutes to 12 minutes.


11) Blue-Green Deployment Failure
Real-Time Scenario
Traffic switched to the new version and users started getting 500 errors.

Root Cause
Health checks not validated properly
Database migration incompatibility
Troubleshooting
Checked ingress logs
Verified application logs
Rolled back immediately
Resolution
Implemented smoke testing
Added automated rollback
Introduced canary deployments

12) Database Migration Failure
Real-Time Scenario
Application deployment succeeded but application crashed after startup.

Root Cause
New application expected updated schema but migration failed.

Resolution
Added migration validation step
Implemented backward-compatible schema changes
Best Practice
Never tightly couple deployments with database schema changes.


